{
    "thig6.7:0.1_0": "Second: Mallikā",
    "thig6.7:0.2_0": "The Book of the Sixes",
    "thig6.7:0.3_0": "Uttarā",
    "thig6.7:1.1_0": "Guttā, you have given up your child,",
    "thig6.7:1.2_0": "your wealth, and all that you love.",
    "thig6.7:1.3_0": "Foster the goal for which you went forth;",
    "thig6.7:1.4_0": "do not fall under the mind’s control.",
    "thig6.7:2.1_0": "Beings deceived by the mind,",
    "thig6.7:2.2_0": "playing in Māra’s domain,",
    "thig6.7:2.3_0": "ignorant, they journey on,",
    "thig6.7:2.4_0": "transmigrating through countless rebirths.",
    "thig6.7:3.1_0": "Sensual desire and ill will,",
    "thig6.7:3.2_0": "and identity view;",
    "thig6.7:3.3_0": "misapprehension of precepts and observances,",
    "thig6.7:3.4_0": "and doubt as the fifth.",
    "thig6.7:4.1_0": "O nun, when you have given up",
    "thig6.7:4.2_0": "these lower fetters,",
    "thig6.7:4.3_0": "you won’t come back",
    "thig6.7:4.4_0": "to this world again.",
    "thig6.7:5.1_0": "And when you’re rid of greed,",
    "thig6.7:5.2_0": "conceit, ignorance, and restlessness,",
    "thig6.7:5.3_0": "having cut the fetters,",
    "thig6.7:5.4_0": "you’ll make an end to suffering.",
    "thig6.7:6.1_0": "Having wiped out transmigration,",
    "thig6.7:6.2_0": "and fully understood rebirth,",
    "thig6.7:6.3_0": "hungerless in this very life,",
    "thig6.7:6.4_0": "you will live at peace.",
    "thig6.7:7.1_0": "... who guard the sense doors are guarded ..."
}